prompt_text: Describe your stay at a friend or relative’s house.
content_text: I always used to visit my relatives house that is my cousin's house. Her name is Annie and she is very lovely. And my dear, dear, dear friend and my sister also. My mother always feel me like my own mother, and she may be different kinds of things for us like. Everything for food and she take care of us a lot even. I felt very comfort table at the home. We used to play table tennis mostly, or badminton outside and. Enjoyed a lot.
